00:09:19.750 --> 00:09:21.100
Tungkol sa kanyang dote,

00:09:21.600 --> 00:09:24.340
gamitin ang Sunwarm Jade.

00:09:30.630 --> 00:09:31.610
Bakit sila nakatingin

00:09:32.430 --> 00:09:33.460
