00:09:38.120 --> 00:09:39.340
Walang kahina-hinala dito.

00:09:52.190 --> 00:09:53.100
Malalim na nagmamalasakit si Master

00:09:53.270 --> 00:09:54.140
para sa pamilya.

00:09:54.920 --> 00:09:56.020
